<div id="test" name="test" class="container tabe-pane fade">
  <section id="test" name="test" class="section-style typewriter-font">
	<h1>AUDIENCE TESTIMONIALS</h1>
        <div style="text-align: left">
	  <p class="testimonial">
&#34Jessica was absolutely brilliant, and her performance exceeded superlatives - she<br />
managed to balance an almost impossible task.&#34
	  </p>
	  <p class="testimonial">
&#34I felt so fed by her courage and wit and stamina. What a writer and actor she is. To be<br/>
able to use both wit and intensity together. She brought me in so close to her. It is<br/>
not an experience I have a lot in the theater. She shared her story without self-pity or<br/>
blame. I couldn't do that. I wish it was more than one night. I would have called all my<br/>
artist friends and told them to go.&#34
	</p>
	<p class="testimonial">
&#34I left the theater feeling exhilarated, emotionally raw, and inspired on so many levels.<br />
I feel that you gave me an incredible gift and I am truly grateful.&#34
	</p>
	<p class="testimonial">
	&#34What an amazing evening. Jessica SHINES on all counts! I have thought of SO many<br/>
	people I would like to see this - because I know they would love it - and learn from it by<br/>
sharing in wounding and healing and the amazing growth/joy that can come out of<br/>
disappointment, fear, suffering. You could tell the audience was right there every second!&#34
	</p>
	<p class="testimonial">
	&#34Thank you for this gift! Your performance was outstanding, you laid out your feelings<br/>
	and emotions for us to touch. You had me in the palm of your hand. Loved it, loved it,<br/>
	loved it. Made me cry - and laugh, too!&#34
	</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
